item.title: All Time Greatest Posts
item.description: All Time Greatest Posts Reserved for all time greatest posts Buzz Aldrin The one thing we should have learned by now is that time and Star Citizen makes fools of us all. The SC faithful have been so sure that total success is just around the corner for so long. And the SC skeptics have been so sure that total collapse has been just around the corner for so long.
